                      <persName ref="PRS10927Makfalta"/> and <persName ref="PRS10928Bakwr"/>, and a deacon, <persName ref="PRS10929TasfaHa"/>, a monk of the <persName ref="PRS11208HouseTakla"/>.
                    The note was written in
                      <date>172 Year of Grace (1512 CE)</date> under the reign of <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe"/> by the priests <persName ref="PRS11004Samuel"/>, <persName ref="PRS11005ZaraM"/>, <persName ref="PRS11006BatraM"/>, 
                    <persName ref="PRS11007Mestafsa"/> and <persName ref="PRS11008Bartalomewos"/> and a several others.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
